STATE of North Carolina
v.
Bobby Tray WYCHE No. 260P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 5, 2018 Kevin P. Bradley, Attorney at Law, for Wyche, Bobby Tray. Jacob Luke Bumm, Attorney at Law, Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, Roger A. Echols, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 20th of August 2018 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Durham County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of December 2018."
